### Usage Notes

**When to validate**:
- Before displaying checkpoint box
- Before ending session
- After creating recovery prompt file

**If validation fails**:
1. Identify missing fields from checklist
2. Add missing information to recovery prompt
3. Re-run validation checklist
4. Only proceed with session end when ALL boxes checked

**Why this matters**:
- Incomplete recovery prompts cause confusion in next session
- Missing next steps = wasted time figuring out what to do
- Missing git commit = can't verify state
- Ensures seamless session continuity
